hadiths[51]{hadithnumber,text}:
3200,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kutton ko qatl karney ka hukm diya, phir farmaya : un logon ko kutton sey kya talluq ? phir ( baad mein) shikari kutta rakhney ki ijazat dey di ."
3201,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kutton ko qatl karney ka hukm diya . phir farmaya : un logon ko kutton sey kya talluq? phir unhen kheti aur baagh (ki rakhwali) key kuttey ki ijazat dey di. (Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) key ustaad Muhammad bin Bashaar) Bundar ney farmaya : aen sey murad Madina key baghaat hain.
3202,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kuttey qatl karney ka hukm diya .
3203,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko buland aawaz key sath kutton key qatl karney ka hukm detey suna , chunanche shikar ya maweshiyon key kuttey key siwa tamam kuttey qatl kar diye jatey they."
3204,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney kutta rakha, uskey amalon sey rozaana eik qeeraat (sawab) kam ho jaeyga. siwaye uskey ke kheti ya maweshiyon (ki hifazat) ka kutta ho."
3205,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar ye baat na hoti ke kuttey bhi (Allah ki makhluq aur) ummaton mein sey eik ummat hain to main unhen qatl karney (aur sab kutton ko khatam kar deney) ka hukm dey deta. (bahar haal) tum bilkul siyah kuttey ko qatl kar diya karo. jo log maweshiyon, shikar ya kheti key kuttey key siwa koi kutta rakhtey hain, unkey sawab mein sey rozaana do qeeraat kam ho jatey hain."
3206,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin abu-Zuhair (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke mainey bani (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : jisney kutta paala, jabke wo usey kheti ya maweshiyon mein faeyda na deta ho, uskey amalon mein sey rozaana eik qeeraat (amal) kam ho jatey hain. un sey kaha gaya : kya aap ney ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey (baraahe-raast) suni hai? unhoney kaha : haan! qism hai us masjid key rab ki!"
3207,"Hazrat Abu-Solba khushni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : main Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huwa, aur arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! hum ehle-kitab key ilaqey mein rehtey hain, unkey bartanon mein kha letey hain. aur shikar key ilaqey mein rehtey hain (hamarey yahan shikar ziyada kya jata hai.) main teer-kamaan sey bhi shikar karta hun, apney sikhaey huye kuttey key sath bhi shikar karta hun aur apney us kuttey key sath bhi shikar kar leta hun jo sikhaya (aur sadhaaya) huwa nahin. (kya ye kaam jayez hain?) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tuney jo bayan kya hai ke tum log ehle-kitab key ilaqey mein rehtey ho to (jawab ye hai ke) unkey bartanon mein na khaya karo, siwaye uskey ke uskey baghair chaara na ho. agar aisi majburi ho to un (bartanon) ko dho kar un mein kha liya karo. aur jo tu ney shikar ki baat ki hai, to jis janwer ko to apni kamaan sey shikar karey is par Allah ka naam ley kar kha ley, aur jo to apney sadhaaey huye kuttey sey shikar kerey. is par Allah ka naam ley kar kha ley, aur jo to apney bin sadhaaey kuttey sey shikar kerey. phir usey zibeh karney ka moqey mil jaey to usey (zibeh kar key) kha ley."
3208,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim Taai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey sawal kya, aur kaha : hum log un kutton key zariey sey shikar kartey hain. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to apney sadhaaey huye kuttey chhodey aur un par Allah ka naam ley to agar wo (shikar ko) qatl kar den to jis (shikar kiye huye janwer) ko wo tumharey liye bacha rakhen, usey to kha sakta hai, siwaye uskey ke kuttey ney (us mein sey kuch) khaya ho. agar kuttey ney khaya ho, tab to na kha kyonkey mujhey ye khatra hai ke usney apney liye pakda hoga. aur agar uskey sath doosrey kuttey bhi shareek hon to phir to na kha. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : mainey apney ustaad Ali bin munzir sey suna, unhoney farmaya : mainey atthawan Haj kiye hain jin mein sey aksar mein pedal safar kya hai."
3209,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamen un , yani majusiyon key kuttey aur perindey key kiye huye shikar sey mana kya gaya hai."
3210,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey kaley siyah kuttey key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : wo shetan hai."
3211,"Hazrat Abu-Solba khushni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jo shikar kamaan key zariey sey hasil ho, wo kha ley."
3212,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Taai) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool! hum log teer chalatey hain (shikar key aadi hain.) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jab to teer chala kar phaad daley to jisey tu ney phada hai, usey kha ley."
3213,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main shikar par teer chalata hun, wo raat bhar mujh sey ghaaieb rehta hai. (agley din milta hai to uska kya hukm hai?) aap ney farmaya : jab tujhey is mein apna teer laga huwa miley aur is mein tujhey uskey siwa kuch aur na miley to kha ley."
3214,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey Meraaz (lohey key phal key bina nokdar lakdi key phal ka teer) sey kiye huye shikar key barey mein daryaft kya to aap ney farmaya : jo uski nauk sey marey, wo kha ley . aur jo uskey chorai key rukh lagney sey marey , usey na kha kyonkey wo chot sey mara huwa janwer hai."
3215,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey meraaz key barey mein daryaft kya to aap ney farmaya : na kha, siwaye uskey ke wo phaad dey ."
3216,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya: agar janwer sey kuch kaat liya jaey jabke wo zinda ho to jo kuch us sey kaata gaya, wo murdar hai."
3217,"Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : aakhiri zamaney mein kuch log hongey jo oonton key kohaan kaat liya kerengey aur bheed bakriyon ki dumein (maslan : dunbey ki chakti) kaat liya kerengey . suno ! zinda ka jo hissa kaata jaey, wo murdar (key hukm mein) hai."
3218,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : hamarey liye do mari hui cheezen halal kar di gaee hain : machli aur tiddi."
3219,"Hazrat Salman (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey tiddi dal key barey mein sawal kya gaya to aap ney farmaya : ye Allah ka sab sey ziyada tadaad wala lashkar hai. main usey na khata hun, na haram kehta hun."
3220,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaaj mutahraat (Raziallahu anhu anhunna) eik dusri ko tiddiyon ki pletein tohfey key tor par bheja karti thin."
3221,"Hazrat Jabir aur Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab tiddi dal key khilaf bad dua farmatey to yun kehtey : aey Allah ! badi tiddiyon ko tabah kar dey, aur chhoti tiddiyon ko maar dal, in key anday kharab kar dey , in ki jad kaat dey , in key munh hamari rozi aur hamara rizq khaney sey band kar dey , be-shak to dua sunney wala hai. eik aadmi ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap kis tarah Allah key eik lashkar ki jad kaatney ki dua kartey hain? aap ney farmaya : tiddi-di-al samandar main eik badi machchhli ki chheenk sey paida hota hai. (hadees key Raavi) Haashim bayan kartey hain ke Ziyad bin Abdullah (Rahimahullah) ney kaha : mujhey eik aadmi ney bataya ke usney machli ki chheenk sey tiddi ko bikharte dekha hai."
3222,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath Haj ya Umerey key liye rawana huye. (raastey mein) tiddi ki eik tukdi samney sey aa gaee. hum unhen apney kodon aur jooton sey maarney lagey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : isey khao, ye bhi samandar key shikar mein shamil hai."
3223,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney mamola, maindak, chewnti aur hud-hud key maarney sey mana farmaya hai."
3224,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chaar janweron ko qatl karney sey mana farmaya, chewnti, shehad ki makkhi, hud-hud aur momlaa."
3225,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : anbiya mein sey eik Nabi ko chewnti ney kaat liya . unkey hukm sey chewntiyon ki basti ko jala diya gaya . Allah ney un ki taraf ""wahi"" ki : tujhey eik chewnti ney kaataa , uski wajeh sey tu ney tasbih karney wali eik qom ko tabah kar diya. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey ye riwayat isi tarah bayan ki. aur (Raavi hadees ney) ( قَرَصَتْهُ ) ki jagah (قَرَصَتْ) key alfaz bayan kiye."
3226,"Hazrat Saeed bin Juber (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) key eik aziz ney kankari phenki. unhoney mana kiya aur farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kankari phainkney sey mana kiya hai aur farmaya hai : ye (kankari) na shikar maarti hai, na dushman ko zakhmi karti hai lekin daant tod deti hai aur aankh phod deti hai. usney dobara yehi harkat ki to Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : main tujhey hadees suna raha hun ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kankari phainkney sey mana kiya hai iskey bawajud tu ney phir wohi harkat ki. main tujh sey kabhi kalam nahin karunga."
3227,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney kankari phainkney sey mana kiya aur farmaya : ye na shikar maarti hai, na dushman ko zakhmi karti hai lekin aankh phod deti hai aur daant tod deti hai."
3228,Hazrat Umme Shareek Ansaariya (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen chhipkaliyon ko maarney ka hukm diya.
3229,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jisney pehli zarab mein chhipkali (ya ghirgit) ko maara , usey itni nekiyan milengi aur jisney usey dusri zarab mein maara, usey itni itni (pehli sey kam) nekiyan milengi aur jisney usey teesri zarab mein maara , usey itni itni (doosri sey kam) nekiyan milengi."
3230,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chhipkali ko fasiq (na farman) farmaya.
3231,"Hazrat Faaka bin Mughira ki azad karda londi Sayeba (Rahimahullah) Alaiha sey riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) key paas gaeen to unkey ghar main eik neza pada huwa dekha. unhoney kaha : Ummul-mominin ! aap is (neze) ka kya karti hain? unhoney farmaya : hum iskey sath chhipkaliyan maartay hain kyonkey hamein Allah key Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bataya hai ke jab Hazrat Ibrahim (Alaihissalam) ko aag mein dala gaya to zamin mein jo bhi janwer tha usney aag bujhaai, siwaye chhipkali key. wo to (aag tez karney key liye) phunkeyn maarti thi, chunanche Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey qatl karney ka hukm diya hai."
3232,Hazrat Abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney har kuchli waley darindey key khaney sey mana farmaya. Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : mainey Sham mein dakhil honey tak ye hadees nahin suni thi.
3233,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har kuchli waley darindey ka khana haram hai."
3234,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney jang khaibar key moqey par har kuchli waley darindey aur har nakhun daar panjey (sey shikar kerney) waley perindey ko khaney sey mana farma diya.
3235,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap sey zamin key (jangli) janweron key barey mein sawal karney key liye hazir huwa hun. aap laumdi key barey mein kya farmatey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : laumdi kon khata hai? mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap bhediye key barey mein kya farmatey hain? aap ney farmaya : kya bhediye ko koi aisa shakhs kha sakta hai jis mein bhalai mojud ho?"
3236,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Abu Ammaar (Rahimahullah) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey lagad-bhaggey key barey mein puchha : kya wo shikar hai? Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ney farmaya : haan. mainey kaha : main usey kha sakta hun? farmaya : haan. mainey kaha : kya ye masla aap ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna hai? farmaya : haan."
3237,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap lagad-bagad key barey mein kya farmatey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : lagad-bagad ko kon khata hai?"
3238,"Hazrat Sabit bin Yazeed Ansaari (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath (safar mein) they. logon ney saandey pakdey aur unhen bhoon kar khaney lagey. mujhey bhi eik saandaa mila, mainey usey bhoonaa aur usey ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney eik chhadi li aur uskey zariey sey us (saandey) ki ungliyan gin'ney lagey, phir farmaya : Bani-Israel ka eik giroh maskh ho kar zamin mein raingney waley janweron ki surat mein tabdeel ho gaya tha. mujhey malum nahin shayad ye wohi qom ho. mainey kaha : log to inhen bhoon kar kha bhi gaey. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney na khaya, na mana farmaya."
3239,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney saandey ko haram qarar nahin diya lekin usey napasand farmaya. aur ye aksar charwaahon ki khurak hai. Allah uskey zariey sey kaee logon ko faeyda deta hai. agar merey paas (saanda) hota to main usey kha leta. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney eik dusri sanad sey bhi mazkura baala hadees key hum maana ye riwayat bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey bayan ki hai."
3240,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaz sey farigh huye to as-haabe-suffa mein sey eik aadmi ney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko mukhatib kar key kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hamarey ilaqey mein saandey bahut hotey hain. aap ka saandon key barey mein kya khayal hai? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke ye eik qom thi jo maskh kar di gaee. chunanche aap ney na usey khaney ka hukm diya, na us sey mana farmaya."
3241,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) ney Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat ki ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhuna huwa saandaa pesh kiya gaya aur (khana khaney key waqt) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key samney rakha gaya. aap ney khaney key liye uski taraf haath badhaya to haazirin ney arz kiya : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye saandey ka gosht hai, chunanche aap ney us sey haath utha liya. Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya saandaa haram hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : nahin, ye merey ilaqey mein nahin hota tha, isliye main is sey karaahat mehsus karta hun. Hazrat Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ney saandey ki taraf haath badha kar is mein sey kuchh khaya aur Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen dekh rahey they."
3242,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney saandey key barey mein farmaya : main haram nahin kehta."
3243,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum maqame marruz-zohraan sey guzrey. (wahan) hamney eik khargosh ko (uski panah gaah sey) nikala. (qafiley key afrad) uskey peechhey bhagey (lekin) wo thak gaey (aur pakad na sakey). mainey taaqqub kar key usey pakad liya aur usey Hazrat abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) key paas ley gaya. unhoney isey zibeh kiya aur uski raan aur pusht ka gosht Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhej diya. aap ney isey qubul farma liya."
3244,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Safwan (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke wo do khargosh (haath mein) latkaaey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key paas sey guzrey aur kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! ye do khargosh merey haath lagey hain, merey paas inhen zibeh karney key liye lohey ki koi chiz (chhuri waghaira) nahin thi, chunanche mainey unhen eik pathar key sath zibeh kar liya. kya main inhen kha lun? aap ney farmaya : kha ley."
3245,"Hazrat Khuzaima bin Juz (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! main aap sey zamin key chhotey (jangli) janweron key barey mein daryaft karney key liye hazir huwa hun. aap saandey key barey mein kya farmatey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main usey nahin khata aur usey haram bhi qarar nahin deta . mainey kaha : jis chiz ko aap haram qarar nahin detey , main usey kha lunga. lekin Allah key Rasool ! (aap) kyon (nahin khatey)? aap ney farmaya : eik qom laapata ho gaee thi. aur mujhey aisi (zahiri) shakal aur surat nazar aai jis sey mujhey shak huwa (ke shayad Bani-Israel ki maskh shuda qom yehi ho). mainey kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! aap khargosh key barey mein kya farmatey hain? Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : main usey nahin khata , aur usey haram bhi qarar nahin deta . mainey kaha : jis chiz ko aap haram qarar nahin detey , main usey kha lunga. lekin , aey Allah key Rasool ! (aap) kyon (nahin khatey)? aap ney farmaya : mujhey bataya gaya hai ke usey khoon (haiz) aata hai."
3246,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : samandar ka pani paak karney wala hai aur uska mara huwa janwer halal hai. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : mujhey Abu-Ubaida Jawwaad (Rahimahullah) sey ye riwayat pahunchi hai ke unhoney farmaya : ye hadees aadha ilm hai, isliye ke duniya bar aur bahar (khsuhki aur samandar) par mushtamil hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney (is hadees key zariey sey) samandar key barey mein fatwa dey diya, baqi khushki reh gaee (ke khushki key kon sey janwer haram hain aur kon sey halal)."
3247,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz ko samandar bahar phenk dey, ya pani us sey peechhey hat jaey (aur wo pani sey bahar reh janey ki wajeh sey mar jaey), usey kha lo aur jo is mein mar kar teer aaye usey na khaao."
3248,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : kowey ko kon kha sakta hai jabke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney uska naam, fasiq,  rakh diya hai? Allah ki qism ! wo paak chizon mein shamil nahin."
3249,"Ummul-mominin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya , sanp fasiq hai, bichchhu fasiq hai, chuhiyaa fasiq hai aur kawwa fasiq hai. Qasim bin Muhammad bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) sey sawal kiya gaya : kya kawwa khaya jata hai? unhoney kaha : jab Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney isey fasiq keh diya to phir usey kon kha sakta hai?"
3250,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney billi ko aur uski qeemat ko khaney sey mana farmaya."
